data.description: Move right in and live your best life with this well maintained, maintenance free, updated condo in the heart of downtown Cleveland. This home boasts 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths with beautiful views of Lake Erie and Browns Stadium. Walk through the front door and enjoy the open floor plan. Kitchen has granite countertops and stainless steel appliances are included. Dining area to enjoy entertaining family and friends. Convenient in unit washer and dryer. Family room with picturesque windows of the lake, full bathroom and bedroom/office with lots of storage. Upstairs enjoy a private master bedroom with a walk in closet and ensuite bathroom. Downtown living at it's finest with a rooftop deck to witness some of the most beautiful sunsets, concerts, football games, fireworks etc that Cleveland has to offer. Walking distance to restaurants, entertainment, shops and more. Easy access to highways. Don't miss out, Call to schedule a private showing with me or your favorite real estate agent.
